  "detailed_description": "Wizard War VR is a MOBA magic shooting game!<br />\r\nDestroy enemy's flag behind the wall using variety of magics!<br />\r\nCooperate with your teammates to defeat enemy!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMagics can be cast by swinging your hand to forward, backward, left, right, up and down.<br />\r\nEach gesture provides skills of different elements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is shop system for both mods. You must get credits from your actions.<br />\r\nWith credit, it's available to upgrade, buy weapons,<br />\r\nget professions, and enhanced yourself.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe support two game mods, which are MOBA and 1:1 Death Match.<br />\r\nFor MOBA mod, each team could have 3 members, and for 1:1 mod, you have 5 rounds to achieve victory!",
  "about_the_game": "Wizard War VR is a MOBA magic shooting game!<br />\r\nDestroy enemy's flag behind the wall using variety of magics!<br />\r\nCooperate with your teammates to defeat enemy!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMagics can be cast by swinging your hand to forward, backward, left, right, up and down.<br />\r\nEach gesture provides skills of different elements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is shop system for both mods. You must get credits from your actions.<br />\r\nWith credit, it's available to upgrade, buy weapons,<br />\r\nget professions, and enhanced yourself.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe support two game mods, which are MOBA and 1:1 Death Match.<br />\r\nFor MOBA mod, each team could have 3 members, and for 1:1 mod, you have 5 rounds to achieve victory!",
